text: Joonas Alanne (born December 5, 1990) is a Finnish ice hockey player. He is currently playing with the Asia League Ice Hockey team the Nikko Ice Buckshttps://www.icebucks.jp/players/9894. Alanne formerly played for the Lahti Pelicans in the Finnish Liiga. Alanne made his Liiga debut playing with Lahti Pelicans during the 2013–14 Liiga season. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Finnish ice hockey forwards Category:Lahti Pelicans players Category:Nikkō Ice Bucks players
